Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:43.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Palti, mis, tuero, moro. Ru, spincio, tirato, cul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:08.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear about this road?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:15.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the other day at Polson's Tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:18.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Were there any rumors about wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:20.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've heard some of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I only chose this road because I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:39.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me. Or do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:44.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:52.50,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and a Shepherds Lamb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:58.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from raising sheep, I can drive away wolves, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:04.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hire me, I can protect you from the wolves on your journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:08.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:27.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for a bit, I'm going to ask my companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Skilled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:33.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's skilled as a shepherd, then it's worth giving her a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, having you is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:45.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's never been the concept of having a shepherd as an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It might become a new business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:53.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Human males are fine with any number of females.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't seduced by her charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, you're a lot cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you just made the passing mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how are her skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:15.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you could be more specific?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I would hunt her sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:24.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But she could surely handle normal wolves easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's rather skilled at handling dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:36.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Troublesome shepherds must have a clever dog, and they must work in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she fulfills those two requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's young if you listen to her voice, but she's to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I might as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to hire her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:05:02.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hire her, that means she'll be traveling with us for a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I {\i1}don't{\i0} want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:11.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only two days until we reach Rubinheigen, is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sorry, but just bear with it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have to bear with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:27.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I simply want to test if a shepherd would be useful as an escort from wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but wouldn't you be troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we travel with others...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if they found out about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted me to say this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:54.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"I just want it to be us two."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:57.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:58.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's only two days, I'm sure she won't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How does forty Trie for escorting us to Rubinheigen sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:20.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If wolves actually attack, and we come out safe, we'll consider that an additional fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too little?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:27.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nora Allent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been a shepherd for a long time now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, only about four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:05.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I became a shepherd after picking him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising. What about before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:13.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for letting me stay at a monastery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped aid the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:22.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,While I aided them, I wondered to myself if I could also work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fortunate that I met Enik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the reward of your daily prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:34.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can't help but think that it's the work of God that brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:43.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met him, he was hurt and full of injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,From wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it was because of bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:54.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He had this staff in his mouth, and he was sitting near the bottom of a hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to find a shepherd offering to be an escort, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Shepherds wouldn't normally do this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:09.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I just wanted to talk to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:15.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I want to be a tailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a partner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:32.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you might earn more by escorting merchants than by being a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Disputes over land must be tough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:41.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, all safe places already have a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only popular places and places full of wolves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:48.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolves are troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're also sly and tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They might be listening from somewhere, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:18.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you stop so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:24.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I know that shepherds sleep as early as possible, when the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:27.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to look after them all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:32.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wonder to myself while looking at their wool,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of clothes will be made from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, your work ethic is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:47.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With your skill, they should have let you taken care of even more sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:51.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even this many was a blessing from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly take care of so many sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they don't have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How about switching employers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:09.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, as merchants are creatures that tend to think about the loss and gain of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Does changing employers happen often?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:21.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like the conditions, it's normal to search for a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:26.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but is your employer the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:30.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A merchant's intuition, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:36.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a priest from the church entrusted me with these sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, they care for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:47.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pay may be minor, but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as God doesn't abandon us, the church won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:56.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't lose your job, and you won't have any trouble finding food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:06.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, it's not like God disallows having a side job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:11.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we reach Rubinheigen, I'll ask a few merchants I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether they need a reliable escort, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:17.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a tough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to maintain my tail every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're talking about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Nora Allent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:43.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's why I asked you first, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even groom my tail in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it hard for you to groom in the wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:06.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were having a lively conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With Nora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:11.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can't have a lively conversation with a dog, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:16.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to talk, so there was no reason to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:20.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's been a while since I was able to talk with a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:24.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not notice that she didn't like talking with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's also possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:35.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs39}If she simply fell for me right away, it would be boring without gradually growing fonder for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:48.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't suit you! It doesn't suit you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to laugh that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:07.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite the trump card you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine if it cleared up your mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:15.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's like I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a gift from that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:57.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been a regular inspection, it would've taken ten times longer to get through, even with a pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I work for the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, here's your promised forty Trie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:10.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I were to exchange this, it would be around forty-five Trie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an investment from a greedy merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:13.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Investment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could have a relationship with a skilled shepherd,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to find some profitable wool for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:28.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be with the Rowen Trading Guild's firm for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you plan to head out to the fields with your sheep again, please come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to introduce you to some merchants who need an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:42.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I should ask you, is the road that we took the only one you could escort people on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:46.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can escort on Casraat, Polson, and Ramtra too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramtra? {\i1}That {\i0}Ramtra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the regular, long-winding route, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I use the shortcut through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:00.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That eerie forest that even knights fear to approach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely fine with Enik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's a good chance you'll have employers, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, the entrance for livestock is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just have to pass through customs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:28.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and sell this armor you got for us at a high price at the Remerio Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll buy honey-preserved peaches with that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up on them being sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a higher chance of their {\i1}not {\i0}being sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act sad if you don't get any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:54.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was used to defend against enemies during war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That hole is used to pour down boiling oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:59.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is strangely particular about defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pass, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:11.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You came from Polson? What's your cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:13.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, twenty complete sets of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Armor? From Polson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:16.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I bought them from the Ratpearon Company. Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will your tax payment be in cash or goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, in goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Go over there, split the armor into groups, and hand it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:40.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that rare to be buying from Polson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. The opposite, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:53.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:59.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Government officials aren't likable everywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:05.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That last government official laughed a bit through his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:08.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After he looked at the mountain of armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:12.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}he was probably thinking you merchants shouldn't get too conceited just because you earned some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:17.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay. We got into the town safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the wagon at the inn and go to the street stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, another beer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty strong, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:07.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you got yourself an expensive girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm jealous since she's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:12.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be perfect if she didn't have a tail, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:19.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The beer is good, and additionally, it's a lively city, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let your guard down since it's lively, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get into disputes with any knights or mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you take care of it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, there's some around your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a point in taking me to that firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be dangerous to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cute, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:05.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get drunk and expose your ears and tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:10.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd just bite onto you and run away from the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can jump over that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:17.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there was an old tale like that with a knight and maiden, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:20.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The one where the knight embraces the maiden and runs away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:27.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that'd make a nice picture, but there's no romance in having a wolf like you bite onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}refuse {\i0}to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were the one that was captured, it wouldn't be worth saving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Businesses tend to have accidents, and dangers follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:45.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like no one will protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Much like how a knight feels safe with his armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:52.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we merchants protect each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:56.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Where we're heading is the original branch of the merchant organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The buildings in my hometown were all like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:10.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice that there are hometowns here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:15.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll go take care of business, so wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:20.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Weren't you going to take me and boast to your colleagues about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:24.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over quickly. If you wait here obediently, I'll buy you some sweet bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:26.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you come here for, you terrible merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:52.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming at this time? Don't you have any motivation to earn money or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just become a thief already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:59.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Great merchants don't have a single speck of dirt on their shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing they dirty are their fingertips with black ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:07.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Running around the market all day is the mark of a third-rate merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a better talker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:14.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop calling me son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:26.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the Rowen Trading Guild is like a son or daughter to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:32.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I know you wet the bed when you were camping on your travels!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:35.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I also know that you trembled and wet yourself in the mansion halls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:38.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,when you stole the proceeds with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:41.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I got it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:53.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a traveling merchant named Lawrence come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:22:00.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lawrence{\i0}? Not even a single rat has set foot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:19.97,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:25.35,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.53,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:33.27,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:35.83,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:41.26,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:46.59,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.93,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.56,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:57.62,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:02.58,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:07.67,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:10.24,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:13.68,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:17.54,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:18.89,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:23.18,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:29.07,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:32.72,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:43.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Swirling Conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:49.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Swirling Conspiracy
